metadata.name: Herbal T Club Mystery Bag
metadata.description:
Herbal T Club is a project with herbal tea as the theme, 3800 shapes are in the Ethereum blockchain.

These accessories and shapes emerge after careful discussion and thinking by digital painters and designers, and designed with their unique style. Add different types of styles and elements, the objective is to make each shape full of its uniqueness.

Herbal T Club is the first NFT project to use cartoon herbal tea as the shape. It boldly cartoonizes the objects to express its unique style, coupled with bright colors and gorgeous accessories, creating a unique style.

In the future, the shapes will be brought to the real objects.
